\par }{\cf0 Acid Arrow
\par }{\fs20\cf0 Conjuration (Creation) [Acid]
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Level:}{\fs20\cf0  Sor/Wiz 2
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Components:}{\fs20\cf0  V, S, M, F
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Casting Time:}{\fs20\cf0  1 standard action
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Range:}{\fs20\cf0  Long (400 ft. + 40 ft./level)
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Effect:}{\fs20\cf0  One arrow of acid
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Duration:}{\fs20\cf0  1 round + 1 round per three levels
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Saving Throw:}{\fs20\cf0  None
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Spell Resistance:}{\fs20\cf0  No
\par A magical arrow of acid springs from your hand and speeds to its target. You must succeed on a ranged touch attack
 to hit your target. The arrow deals 2d4 points of acid damage with no splash damage. For every three caster levels (to a maximum of 18th), the acid, unless somehow neutralized, lasts for another round, dealing another 2d4 points of damage in that round.

\par }{\i\fs20\cf0 Material Component: }{\fs20\cf0 Powdered rhubarb leaf and an adder\rquote s stomach.
\par }{\i\fs20\cf0 Focus: }{\fs20\cf0 A dart.
\par }{\cf0 
\par Acid Fog
\par }{\fs20\cf0 Conjuration (Creation) [Acid]
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Level:}{\fs20\cf0  Sor/Wiz 6, Water 7
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Components:}{\fs20\cf0  V, S, M/DF
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Casting Time:}{\fs20\cf0  1 standard action
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Range: }{\fs20\cf0 Medium (100 ft. + 10 ft./level)
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Effect:}{\fs20\cf0  Fog spreads in 20-ft. radius, 20 ft. high
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Duration:}{\fs20\cf0  1 round/level
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Saving Throw:}{\fs20\cf0  None
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Spell Resistance:}{\fs20\cf0  No
\par }{\i\fs20\cf0 Acid fog }{\fs20\cf0 creates a billowing mass of misty vapors similar to that produced by a }{\i\fs20\cf0 solid fog }{\fs20\cf0 spell. In addition to slowing creatures down and obscuring sight, this spell\rquote 
s vapors are highly acidic. Each round on your turn, starting when you cast the spell, the fog deals 2d6 points of acid damage to each creature and object within it.
\par }{\i\fs20\cf0 Arcane Material Component:}{\fs20\cf0  A pinch of dried, powdered peas combined with powdered animal hoof.
\par 
\par }{\cf0 Acid Splash
\par }{\fs20\cf0 Conjuration (Creation) [Acid]
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Level:}{\fs20\cf0  Sor/Wiz 0
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Components:}{\fs20\cf0  V, S
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Casting Time:}{\fs20\cf0  1 standard action
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Range:}{\fs20\cf0  Close (25 ft. + 5 ft./2 levels)
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Effect:}{\fs20\cf0  One missile of acid
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Duration:}{\fs20\cf0  Instantaneous
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Saving Throw:}{\fs20\cf0  None
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Spell Resistance:}{\fs20\cf0  No
\par You fire a small orb of acid at the target. You must succeed on a ranged touch attack to hit your target. The orb deals 1d3 points of acid damage.
\par 
